,"msg":"<blockquote>佢都算有心，特登學廣東話唱歌冧香港fans</blockquote><br />\n入鄉隨俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d62b25e74ae8eb3818b59288c2fdca9bcd6cb25","tid":477901,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢都算有心，特登學廣東話唱歌冧香港fans</blockquote><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1810ef648f9590e991364d78d8a9b879f81026f","tid":477901,"uid":92477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:22:19.000Z","msg":"五年冇出廣東歌　鄧紫棋接受超蓮畀挑戰<br />\n<br />\n歌手鄧紫棋（G.E.M.）出席活動，為大會演繹主題曲《Victoria》，她直言已有五年沒有出過廣東歌，接了一個挑戰性大的Project感到期待和開心：「超蓮叫我接呢個任務時好趕，一個月都冇，要將香港有地標性嘅名字擺落歌詞。每個人都發揮小宇宙好快完成，好似極限挑戰咗，而王祖藍係歌詞上都幫咗好多忙。（廣東歌反而有挑戰？）主要有個主題要寫，平時都係寫情歌多，有個限制發揮令我更有感覺，超蓮係咁Check住我進度，不停催好緊張。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/212210_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F212210_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a0ced67a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"753c8466a7ba60b00ffca77e32bbeafef79ea536","tid":477901,"uid":39527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121f2d3013b7de637db0e6d644f0a0b1745d5e0b","tid":477901,"uid":92477,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩放監呀?"}]}